thread.title: TAMMY

author: TAMMY
title: TAMMY
text: Loved the location, but the bedding needs to be replaced badly. The up stairs mattress was very dirty, and as usual the linens didn't seem clean and the fitted sheets never fit!!! I just feel that a little more effort needs to be put in to the cleaning. After all we all pay for the service. Other than that, we love Starrcrest resort, and we have rented from Outrageous 4 times now and will most likely be back!!!
